{"tid":2193672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[嚴重警告]蚑共全方位搞緊分化，呢波勁過之前好撚多，請自己小心","createTime":"2020-09-08T04:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T12:08:31.000Z","uid":48234,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"015ede34af110e479635160ac421338fd8a554ba","tid":2193672,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:22:38.000Z","msg":"老鳳承認自己單兵力量不足<br />\n冇能力用一個account一次過應付大量奶共藍屍/五毛/PR/賤賊/國安<br />\n或者幫助被誤導手足<br />\n對抗呢班打手，需要大家合作<br />\n所以老鳳有提過，單憑一個人整戇鳩list/狗隻list係唔夠<br />\n必須聯同幾個手足各自整list出嚟俾大家參考先有用<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">請各位真正手足保持頭腦清醒<br />\n防範所有分化手足嘅言論</span></span><br />\n<br />\n老鳳必定會俾大量狗隻屈做分化鳥<br />\n但係老鳳一直以來追擊狗隻只有一個原因:<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">極度憎恨蚑那共匪</span></span><br />\n由雨傘運動開始到而家，初心從未改變<br />\n但係如果有狗隻利用老鳳對蚑共嘅憎恨誤導老鳳<br />\n請手足幫一幫手糾正老鳳，攞出足夠證據<br />\n<br />\n因為老鳳搞奶共狗嘅行為太過明顯<br />\n蚑共好明顯已經落晒order用盡方法針對老鳳<br />\n用咗唔知幾撚多個account有組織性咁大量洗板同埋洗老鳳負評<br />\n務求誤導大家，以為奶共先係正確<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">唔好以為手足會咁撚蠢，見到老鳳收大量負評就會同意對家嘅言論<br />\n打倒一個老鳳，仲有千千萬萬個老鳳</span></span><br />\n香港憎恨蚑共嘅手足絕對多過蚑共想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">順便宣傳一套好用連登工具</span></span><br />\n【LIHKG User Script】會員標籤功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a><br />\n<br />\n再匯入power_off手足嘅「戇鳩list」<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1bz9klvGSoiX_oK-i9PM1m1aMBTc8bukQI30NWQcx13Y/edit#gid=831334630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1bz9klvGSoiX_oK-i9PM1m1aMBTc8bukQI30NWQcx13Y%2Fedit%23gid%3D831334630&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=4be49a14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1bz9klvGSoiX_oK-i9PM1m1aMBTc8bukQI30NWQcx13Y/edit#gid=831334630</a><br />\n<br />\n亦可以自行增減各種會員標籤<br />\n不限標籤敵對狗隻，亦可以標籤真正手足"},{"pid":"0898425578244c107ada9462b83500662f24e716","tid":2193672,"uid":48234,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EFd10VZU4AAL7IG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEFd10VZU4AAL7IG.jpg&h=a14d4f79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e84093991fd09d6ca0041814c19662063f40cd39","tid":2193672,"uid":146642,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"笑死人咩 屈毛鳳"},{"pid":"08bfabb217cc422c03d604202d8c6173e174fef6","tid":2193672,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:31:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"becdff273f0fcf095720118d09e7a16eebd348e8","tid":2193672,"uid":17799,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:32:53.000Z","msg":"老鳳做aco好能屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府又然"},{"pid":"a23e73a54c51f4f0f11664d5115f4997ab72803c","tid":2193672,"uid":137604,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"beed38b405774c0d2fa4a47ec7443cf442ecd48b","tid":2193672,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82d0e17d043c861bf1e2762ee60329be915930cc","tid":2193672,"uid":48234,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e84093991fd09d6ca0041814c19662063f40cd39","tid":2193672,"uid":146642,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"笑死人咩 屈毛鳳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:37:29.000Z","msg":"俾老鳳開波追擊嘅<br />\n除咗一毛/三毛/五毛/柒毛/八毛之外<br />\n仲有賤賊、共匪、國安、分化狗、藍屍<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得自己唔屬於狗隻<br />\n你可以抗辯，但係有挑釁行為嘅一概不獲受理直至道歉為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebaa05a9ce6feafef23b857865228d68f320bb5","tid":2193672,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"08bfabb217cc422c03d604202d8c6173e174fef6","tid":2193672,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:31:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:37:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNv9jui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNv9jui.jpg&h=2d820456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n擁有分身證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,等同明確承認開分身 R730(狗隻#137604)<br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/GpbQh7RN/YOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FGpbQh7RN%2FYOU.jpg&h=eacd9956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著他笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"bb83dd74ba854d848ed9c8657f65593c73364569","tid":2193672,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a23e73a54c51f4f0f11664d5115f4997ab72803c","tid":2193672,"uid":137604,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">好撚有pattern喎，開分身證據確鑿<br />\n連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNv9jui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNv9jui.jpg&h=2d820456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問R730(狗隻#137604)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2111627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2111627</a><br />\n此狗隻奶共證據:<br />\n出言侮辱同路人，近日又留言指「聽到仲有人講831，真係好尷尬」。<br />\n建議而家即刻係各大屈臣氏大叫政府無能 馬上封關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eOKtbT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eOKtbT</a><br />\n太子站幕門突然碎裂  玻璃跌入路軌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/atgGEHV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/atgGEHV</a><br />\n<br />\n懷疑此帳號原擁有者可能已經被殺,以前反CCTVB,而家做CCTVB打手<br />\n睇CCTVB死全家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/794788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/794788</a><br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n此狗隻為沙皮狗分身明顯證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,明確承認開分身<br />\n<br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/GpbQh7RN/YOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FGpbQh7RN%2FYOU.jpg&h=eacd9956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成撚日話老鳳洗板,梗係啦,你啲罪證咁撚多,你出現已經等於迫老鳳洗板<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著他笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"423d6cb5b98fd29b18c56d2022bd4832a1097894","tid":2193672,"uid":17799,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"beed38b405774c0d2fa4a47ec7443cf442ecd48b","tid":2193672,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"becdff273f0fcf095720118d09e7a16eebd348e8","tid":2193672,"uid":17799,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:32:53.000Z","msg":"老鳳做aco好能屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府又然"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"我笑老鳳 你們可以屈我毛了<img src=\"/assets/f